programme.desc: Marshtato Fairy / Do The Biggie - On the foggiest night of the year, the Marshtato Fairy magically delivers marshtatos to Troll Village, which every Troll loves and celebrates- except for Branch, who doesn’t think the Marshtato Fairy exists. When Poppy encourages him to believe, Branch set out to prove Poppy wrong. /When Biggie accidentally invents a dance craze, he realizes how much he enjoys being the center of attention. Biggie and Guy set out to create another Troll dance sensation in order to keep Biggie’s big moment going.(n)

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective S1
programme.desc: The Case Of The Blue Wall - Everyone is going to play Hide and Seek in Brickabuild but Fuse stops the game because someone has painted the big wall outside his workshop blue! What if they do it again? Or if they decide to paint the rest of Brickabuild? Noddy uses all his investigating skills of who, what, where, when, why and how to work out that the wall must have been painted by someone very tall who likes the colour blue. Smartysaurus! She admits she painted it so that she could be better at hide-and-seek! Noddy helps her to understand that she can play the game without having to cheat. Thank you Noddy!(n)

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective S1
programme.desc: The Case Of The Fable Forest Gold - The Pirates are searching for the long-lost Fable Forest Gold. If they can't find it they might have to stop being pirates for good! Noddy leaps into action to help them. Using all his investigating skills, asking who, what, where, when, why and how and with the help of the wwwbook Noddy follows the clues and finds the gold! Now the pirates can stay in Toyland and hunt for treasure forever! Hurrah for Noddy!(n)

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion

programme.title: Postman Pat Delivery Service
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Bouncing Bulb - Pat's Special Delivery is a very large, very fragile lighthouse bulb, and everything seems to be conspiring to make him break it! Falling timber, an out of control sofa, Bonnie the dog, high winds...! Pat's journey from the sorting office to Pencaster Bay is a minefield of hazards. Waiting for the bulb is lighthouse keeper Chris Beacon and his pet parrot Micawber, both anxious to get the lighthouse working before sundown, and tracking a storm blowing in. Out at sea are Alf and PC Selby, enjoying a day's fishing, until they drift off-course and need the lighthouse to guide them ashore...(n)

programme.title: Postman Pat Delivery Service
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Lost Pigeon - The Thompson's family pigeon, Cedric, has been reported found in Northern Ireland. Pat must take Dorothy and Bill to help bring him back in the SDS Plane. Meanwhile Alf camps out at the sorting office, pining for his beloved Cedric's return. programme.title: Special
programme.desc: Otto Rehhagel staat bekend om zijn zeer verassende Europese titel met Griekenland in 2004. Maar mischien nog wel een grotere verassing was zijn Bundesligatitel met promovendus 1. FC Kaiserslautern. In deze special wordt teruggeblikt op hoe Rehhagels Kaiserslautern historie schreef, door in twee jaar zowel de 2. Bundesliga als de Bundesliga te winnen.(n)

programme.title: Special
programme.sub-title: Klopp en het sprookje van Mainz
programme.desc: Jürgen Klopp is tegenwoordig succesvol trainer van Liverpool en eerder Borussia Dortmund. Maar zijn eerste successen behaalde hij bij het bescheiden 1. FSV Mainz 05. In deze special blikken we terug op die periode, waarin de markante maar nog onbekende Klopp de eerste stappen in zijn succesvolle trainerscarriére zet.(n)

programme.title: Special
programme.desc: In het seizoen 1992/1993 pakte het Werder Bremen van Otto Rehhagel zeer verassend de Duitse dubbel. Met toenmalige hoofdrolspelers als Marco Bode en Wynton Rufer wordt teruggeblikt op deze unieke prestatie, aan de hand van mooie beelden en memorabele anekdotes.(n)

programme.title: Special
programme.episode-num: In 2013 won Bayern München de drie belangrijkste prijzen: de Duitse Beker, de Bundesliga en de UEFA Champions League. Dit succes wordt vooral toegeschreven aan toenmalig coach Jupp Heynckes. In deze aflevering wordt door onder andere Toni Kroos teruggeblikt op dit, zelfs voor Bayern München, unieke seizoen.
